entries.title: McDaniel vs. Dhillon: Inside the battle for the RNC
entries.description: In interviews with POLITICO, the incumbent chair and her foremost challenger sparred ahead of their Friday election clash.

entries.title: RNC to consider resolution condemning Kanye West, Fuentes and antisemitism writ large
entries.description: The resolution is being introduced by Shawn Steel, a committee member. It comes after Donald Trump’s infamous dinner.

entries.title: Mike Pence had classified documents at home, turned them over
entries.description: In a Jan. 22 letter to the National Archives, Jacob indicated that FBI agents came to Pence’s Indiana home on the night of Jan. 19 to retrieve documents that the former vice president had located a few days earlier.
